snippet.textDisplay:
FIRST OF ALL A VERY VERY GOOD EVENING TO ALL OF MY FRIENDS THOSE ARE IN THIS DISCUSSION PLATFORM AND FORGIVE ME FOR SUCH A LONG TALK SO PLEASE BEAR WITH ME .AFTER HEARING THIS SONG WITH A HEAVY HEART I WANT TO KEEP SOME OF MY OPINION.

RANGABATI...... IS A SAMBALPURI FOLK SONG WAS RECORDED DURING MID 1970 .THIS SONG IS A MIRROR IMAGE OF WESTERN ODISHA ( SAMBALPURI CULTURE). THIS SONG INCLUDES EMOTION, FILLING, DAY TO DAY LIFE OF WESTERN ODISHA PEOPLE .IT IS NOT ONLY A SONG BUT MORE THEN A MILESTONE .TILL NOW ALSO IT IS AN OUTLOOK OF WESTERN ODISHA .

BUT IN THIS REMAKE THE GUYS TOTALLY RUINED THE BEAUTY OF THE SONG.I DONT KNOW IN WHOSE MIND SUCH A DIRTY IDEA OF REMAKING BORN BUT ANY WAY DAMN SURELY HE OR SHE MUST BE A ENEMY OF OUR CULTURE .I WOULD LIKE TO ASK THAT FELLOW HOW MUCH HE OR SHE WANT TO EARN BY SUCH DIRTY JOB. 

FRIENDS THOSE HAVE GIVEN THERE WORTHY COMMENTS SUPPORTING THIS REMAKE FOR THEM I WOULD SAY...THEY REALLY DONT KNOW TRUE WESTERN ODISHA CULTURE OR SAMBALPURI LANGUAGE .IT IS TOTALLY DIFFERENT FROM ODIA IN PRONUNCIATION. YOU PEOPLE DONT LOVE YOUR MOTHER LAND AND MOTHER TONGUE. NOT AT ALL. OTHERWISE U WILL NEVER SUPPORT SUCH FELLOWS WHO IS TRYING TO SPOIL YOUR ANCIENT TREASURE.

FOR RITU RAJ AND SONA... I WAS A GRATE FAN OF YOU AND ALWAYS RESPECTING YOUR TALENT. BUT NOW I THINK I WAS JUST OVER ESTIMATING ABOUT YOU .AT LEAST YOU SHOULD DO SOME HOME WORK ABOUT SAMBALPURI LANGUAGE BEFORE KEEPING IT IN A NATIONAL LEVEL PLATFORM .SUCH ACTIVITY RUINS YOUR PERSONALITY.

FOR BOTH IDIOT RAPPERS...I JUST WANT TO ASK U.....WHERE HAVE U COME FROM.ARE U REALLY INDIAN???????

FOR COKE STUDIO......... I WAS ALWAYS THINKING THAT IT IS A PRODUCER OF GRATE SONGS. FOR ME IT IS NOT ONLY A STUDIO BUT ALSO A FULL VERSION ENTERTAINMENT PLANT. BUT FOR INNOVATION END EXPERIMENT IS THIS THE ONLY WAY.I AM AFRAID THAT SUCH ACTIVITY WILL HAMPER ITS REPUTATION.SO I REQUEST KINDLY COME OUT OF SUCH BUSINESS.

FINALLY AGAIN SORRY FOR SUCH  LONG OPINION. ACTUALLY IT HURTED ME SO DEEPLY THAT I COULD NOT STOP MYSELF.MY DEAR FRIENDS KINDLY DONT KILL OUR CULTURE IN THE NAME OF MODERNIZATION. LETS SAVE OUR INCREDIBLE CULTURE AND SUCH BEAUTIFUL TREASURE. 

THANKS FOR READING AND HAVE A NICE DAY...........

snippet.textDisplay: To all those who are complaining about the song being killed, please know that coke studio is an experiment in fusion music. First learn what "fusion-music" means. If you don't like fusion then don't come to this page for music. Of course this song is a folk song, but the whole point of fusion is to fuse with a totally different genre. Personally, the western touch to this is superb and I am saying this from the point of view of someone who has learnt music in the heart of the western region of Odisha. Finally, feel really proud that MTV finally features a Sambalpuri song when no one in the country gives a shit about Sambalpur. Thanks to MTV, Ram Sampath and co. for creating this beautiful piece.
snippet.textOriginal: To all those who are complaining about the song being killed, please know that coke studio is an experiment in fusion music. First learn what "fusion-music" means. If you don't like fusion then don't come to this page for music. Of course this song is a folk song, but the whole point of fusion is to fuse with a totally different genre.
